100
00:09:50,775 --> 00:09:52,415
<i>Landing pad is cleared</i>

101
00:10:05,336 --> 00:10:07,136
<i>Bravo, coming back.</i>

102
00:10:09,256 --> 00:10:11,296
Good to go, Griggs.

103
00:10:15,216 --> 00:10:16,976
- Dr. Halvorson?
- Yes?

104
00:10:17,737 --> 00:10:19,777
- Welcome to Thule.
- Thank you.

105
00:10:19,897 --> 00:10:23,097
Edvard asked you to go
to the site, right now.

106
00:10:24,337 --> 00:10:26,057
Lars is going to drive you.

107
00:10:27,697 --> 00:10:29,137
- Hi.
- Hi. Welcome.

108
00:10:29,217 --> 00:10:31,057
<i>- Please go in the Spryte.
- Thanks.</i>

109
00:10:31,137 --> 00:10:32,377
Hello, sir.

110
00:11:28,061 --> 00:11:29,301
