162
00:16:15,183 --> 00:16:19,952
- Sorry, I didn't mean to keep you up.
- No, no, it's fine.

163
00:16:24,293 --> 00:16:27,064
I'll never look at them the same again.

164
00:17:10,687 --> 00:17:12,527
What do you mean for transport weight?

165
00:17:12,647 --> 00:17:18,167
