It broke out!

214
00:24:27,599 --> 00:24:29,039
What?

215
00:24:29,799 --> 00:24:31,799
It ain't a damn joke, man!

216
00:24:31,879 --> 00:24:34,119
The freaking thing's alive!

217
00:24:34,919 --> 00:24:37,199
I was in the room, man,
looking at the ice

218
00:24:37,279 --> 00:24:38,919
then the freaking thing jumped out!

219
00:25:03,161 --> 00:25:05,441
We search
in groups of two and three.

220
00:25:06,481 --> 00:25:08,921
The entire camp.
If you find it, pull out,

221
00:25:08,922 --> 00:25:10,722
don't attempt anything
on your own.

222
00:25:11,231 --> 00:25:12,390
And be careful...

223
00:25:12,551 --> 00:25:14,101
we don't know what condition it's in.

224
00:26:03,894 --> 00:26:07,335
Griggs, did you leave that open?

225
00:26:09,780 --> 00:26:13,257
- I don't remember.
- Shit.

226
00:26:18,227 --> 00:26:21,887
Hey, just be careful, man. That thing
jumped through the fucking roof.

227
00:26:49,129 --> 00:26:50,129
Jesus Christ.

228
00:27:57,903 --> 00:27:59,893
Help! Over here!

229
00:28:01,203 --> 00:28:03,895
Help! Somebody! Over here!

230
00:28:06,295 --> 00:28:08,895
- It attacked Henrik.
- Come on.

231
00:28:12,295 --> 00:28:15,895
- Jesus!
- In there!

232
00:28:21,296 --> 00:28:22,896
- God, somebody do something!
- Oh my God.

233
00:28:27,896 --> 00:28:29,896
Shoot it! Shoot the fucker, man!

234
00:28:51,897 --> 00:28:53,597
We got to burn that fucker, man! Burn it!

235
00:29:00,699 --> 00:29:01,599
Throw it, throw it!

236
00:29:58,703 --> 00:29:59,803
His blood pressure's low.

237
00:30:07,703 --> 00:30:09,503
Henrik and...
his small children.

238
00:30:13,274 --> 00:30:16,704
Yes, it's horrible.
It's a horrible tragedy.

239
00:30:18,274 --> 00:30:21,704
We're all shocked.
At what happened to Henrik.

240
00:30:23,174 --> 00:30:26,804
But with due respect, we need to examine
the remains before it all disintegrates.

241
00:30:27,674 --> 00:30:29,805
Hey, that was a man.
Not remains.

242
00:30:30,006 --> 00:30:31,806
No, I know,
I'm talking about the creature.

243
00:30:32,875 --> 00:30:36,005
And I'm sure we're all aware
of the importance of this discovery.

244
00:30:36,175 --> 00:30:37,905
This may be the first
and only time...

245
00:30:37,906 --> 00:30:40,606
