by an alien lifeform.

246
00:30:41,175 --> 00:30:44,877
And as scientists,
we're obliged to study it.

247
00:30:44,878 --> 00:30:48,078
Didn't work out so well
the last time, did it?

248
00:30:48,377 --> 00:30:49,907
I think you should destroy it.

249
00:30:52,077 --> 00:30:53,196
Completely.

250
00:30:54,677 --> 00:30:56,877
I think you've contributed
enough to this matter now.

251
00:30:57,378 --> 00:30:58,478
Oh, really?

252
00:30:59,216 --> 00:31:02,696
Listen, your guy, Olav, back there,
he's in bad shape.

253
00:31:04,077 --> 00:31:06,597
Now, we're gonna fly him back
to McMurdo at sun-up...

254
00:31:06,598 --> 00:31:08,298
